### Patient Login
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "patient@example.com",
  "password": "Patient123!"
}

### Search for doctors by specialty
GET http://localhost:8080/api/patient/doctors?specialty=Cardiology&page=0&size=5&sort=yearsOfExperience,desc
Authorization: Bearer {{PATIENT_TOKEN}}

### Get available slots for selected doctor
GET http://localhost:8080/api/patient/doctors/{{DOCTOR_ID}}/slots?page=0&size=5
Authorization: Bearer {{PATIENT_TOKEN}}

### Book appointment
POST http://localhost:8080/api/patient/{{PATIENT_ID}}/appointments
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{PATIENT_TOKEN}}

{
  "slotId": {{SLOT_ID}},
  "patientId": {{PATIENT_ID}}
}

### Verify booked appointments
GET http://localhost:8080/api/patient/{{PATIENT_ID}}/appointments?page=0&size=5&sort=slot.startTime,desc
Authorization: Bearer {{PATIENT_TOKEN}}
